<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
        <title>Flora Hotels</title>
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@4.6.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-xOolHFLEh07PJGoPkLv1IbcEPTNtaed2xpHsD9ESMhqIYd0nLMwNLD69Npy4HI+N" crossorigin="anonymous">
        <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
    </head>
    <body>
        <header>
            <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-light bg-light">
                <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNavAltMarkup">
                    <div class="navbar-nav">
                        <a class="nav-link " href="Home.html">Home <span class="sr-only">(current)</span></a>
                        <a class="nav-link" href="Deals.html">Deals</a>
                        <a class="nav-link" href="#">Managing Bookings</a>
                        <a class="nav-link" href="About Us.html">About Us</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <a class="navbar-brand" href="#">
                    <img src="img/FLORA HOTELS LOGO.png" width="156" height="183" alt="Flora Hotels Logo">
                </a>
                <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#navbarNavAltMarkup" aria-controls="navbarNavAltMarkup" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
                    <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
                </button>
            </nav>
        </header>
        <main class="Standard-room">
            <div class="container-standard">
                <div class="standard-upper">
                    <h2>{{ rooms[0].name }}</h2>
                    <h4>£{{ rooms[0].price }}/night</h4>
                </div>
                <div id="carouselExampleIndicators" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel" >
                    <ol class="carousel-indicators">
                        <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
                        <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="1"></li>
                        <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="2"></li>
                    </ol>
                    <div class="carousel-inner">
                        <div class="carousel-item active">
                            <img src="img/standard hotel room2.png" class="d-block w-100" alt="standard room">
                        </div>
                        <div class="carousel-item">
                            <img src="img/Standard Toilet.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="premium room">
                        </div>
                        <div class="carousel-item">
                            <img src="img/Standard Balcony.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="exclusive room">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide="prev">
                        <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                        <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
                    </button>
                    <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide="next">
                        <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                        <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
                    </button>
                </div>
                <p>Our {{ rooms[0].name }} offers a combination of both comfort and convenience, designed to cater to the needs of our customers. With a size of approximately {{ rooms[0].size }}, this room features a {{ rooms[0].bed }}, making it ideal for people looking for a {{ rooms[0].audience_purpose }}. Whether you're here for business or a vacation, the {{ rooms[0].name }} provides a relaxing environment, complete with a spacious balcony facing stunning views, ensuring an enjoyable stay at Flora Hotels.</p>
                <a href="">Reviews ></a>
            </div>
            <div class="map">
                <h1>Map</h1>
            </div>
            <div class="embed-responsive embed-responsive-16by9" style="position:relative;bottom:6em;">
                <iframe class="embed-responsive-item" src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d2424.278469535016!2d-0.12775818437936752!3d51.507350216892185!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x48761b2cbe1e8d7b%3A0x7436b93fae29dbfd!2sLondon!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sus!4v1617165749263!5m2!1sen!2sus" allowfullscreen>
                </iframe>
            </div>
            <div class="after-map">
                <div class="after-map-pt1">
                    <p>Bed & Breakfast</p>
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-outline-secondary" style="margin-left:10px; margin-bottom:5px">Select</button>
                </div>
                <div class="after-map-pt2">
                    <p>All Inclusive</p>
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-outline-secondary" style="margin-left:68px; margin-bottom:5px">Select</button>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="Book-Now">
                <h2>Book Now</h2>
                <div class="Book-Now-Container">
                    <div style="display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between;">
                        <p><strong>Nights</strong></p>
                        <p><strong>Price</strong></p>
                    </div>
                    <div style="display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between;">
                        <p>{{ booking[0].nights | int}} nights</p>
                        <p>£{{ booking[0].nights * rooms[0].price | int }}</p>
                    </div>
                    <div style="display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between;">
                        <p>{{ booking[0].meal_deal}}</p>
                        <p>£{{ all_inclusive * booking[0].nights | int }}</p>
                    </div>
                    <hr style="border: 1px solid black; width: 100%; margin: 10px 0;">
                    <div style="display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between;">
                        <p>Total</p>
                        <p>£{{ (booking[0].nights * rooms[0].price) + (all_inclusive * booking[0].nights) | int }}</p>
                    </div>
                    <hr style="border: 1px solid black; width: 100%; margin: 10px 0;">
                    <div style="display: flex; justify-content: center; margin-top: 20px;color: rgb(56, 90, 56);">
                        <a href="Confirm Booking.html" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg active" role="button" aria-pressed="true" style="width: 50%;">Book</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

        </main>
        <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/jquery@3.5.1/dist/jquery.slim.min.js" integrity="sha384-DfXdz2htPH0lsSSs5nCTpuj/zy4C+OGpamoFVy38MVBnE+IbbVYUew+OrCXaRkfj" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
        <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@4.6.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-Fy6S3B9q64WdZWQUiU+q4/2Lc9npb8tCaSX9FK7E8HnRr0Jz8D6OP9dO5Vg3Q9ct" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    </body>
</html>